Package org.red5.io.rtp

Class AV1Packetizer

java.lang.Object
org.red5.io.rtp.AV1Packetizer
public class AV1Packetizer extends Object
AV1 packetizer provides methods to packetize and depacketize AV1 payloads.
Author:
Paul Gregoire
See Also:
